{"type": "article", "id": 2909, "title": "旅行咖啡套装", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-17T08:04:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232352DE8MFinSX5R3Ql9U.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t对于真正的咖啡爱好者来说，一杯手工调制的咖啡是日常必需品。最近，设计团队 Timbuk2 联手咖啡连锁品牌 Blue Bottle Coffee ，推出了一款旅行咖啡套装，包括一款不锈钢材质的手摇式研磨机、两只搪瓷咖啡杯、滤杯以及滤纸。为了让用户在旅途中更加方便收纳，设计团队为此专门制作了一个帆布收纳包。定价 179 美元，<a href=\"https://www.timbuk2.com/blue-bottle-coffee-travel-kit/201.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232350cpQXotus0h5xaePI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232351J6UNFaApWmcrwdxD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523235153oLNaGRm0c4Sy2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323523lCSfjFnNmDKQq2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}